Core features

1. A task to have three properties, name, description, status
2. There can be 2 status, to do and done
3. user can drag and drop one task from one status to another status
4. store the data into localstorage/sessionstorage to persist after refresh

UI model

1. Page upper section to have two i/p fields, name and description and a create button to create a task. default status is to do (Done)
2. once created, i/p fields to be emptied and a task to get added to the to do list (Done)
3. In the middle to lower section, two vertical list should be present which contains the tasks of two status todo and done (Done)
4. The task data to be persisted after refresh


